extendedInfo.description: - CCNA is one of the most famous networking certification over the world. It will be a good way to boost your career by earning it- This is a great application for Android that allows candidate to practice for the CCNA certification exam.App features: There are three main functions focusing on program:- Training The questions are categorized according to the main topics in the CCNA program to streng then candidates' knowledge In this section, candidate can choose the number of questions in order or random, set the countdown timer for each practicing item.- Exam Candidate will have the opportunity to test with the number of questions in the same time as the CCNA exam. After completing, the result will be notified immediately- History Candidate can review the result of previous examThere are three types of questions that app can support: - Single choice - Multiple choice - Matchingquestion: Same as drag-and-drop question in the CCNA examSpeed up your career and make your CCNA exam easier with the CCNA training app as your guideIf you experience any problems with this application, may contact us at the email address: quiz@dft.vn
